A certain young MAGA kept posting
While his lungs the covid was roasting.
He coulda been vaxed,
But he'd rather be axed.
Now his social accounts are all ghosting.

#Covid_19 #CovidVaccine #CovidLimerick #CoronaLimerick #poem 

A certain young MAGA recovered
From a case of the covid he suffered.
No lesson he learned,
And the vax he then spurned,
And back on the vent he's discovered.
